data.description: Check out this  single story, 1574 s.f, 3 bedroom + den, 2 full bath, located in premier subdivision ''Glennwilde Groves'', with two community pools, Pacana Park, close-in to shopping, grade schools within walking distance, makes this an ideal location within the fastest growing community in Arizona! Home features: Over sized tile, upgraded cabinets, fans and blinds throughout, Water Softener+R/O system, huge greatroom, with den , 2 large secondary rooms, with extra large Master bedroom/ bathroom, beautiful landscape front and back, with Community park across the street. Put this on your list today!
